{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Place a jug onto mixing bowl lid, then weigh extra virgin olive oil into it. Set jug aside.","Place lemon zest, Parmesan cheese and garlic into mixing bowl and mill <b>10 sec\/speed 9<b>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula.","Add lemon juice, pine nuts, basil leaves and salt and mix <b>4 sec\/speed 5<b>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula.","Mix <b>speed 3<b>, adding reserved oil through hole in mixing bowl lid. Transfer pesto into a bowl and set aside.","Place water into mixing bowl. Place Varoma dish into position, then line Varoma dish with baking paper. Place unwrapped Brie or Camembert into Varoma dish.","Insert Varoma tray, then weigh tomatoes onto it. Secure Varoma lid and steam <b>14-16 min\/Varoma\/speed 1<b>, or until cheese is soft and melted in the center.","Pour reserved pesto onto a serving platter, then place melted cheese carefully on top. Arrange steamed tomatoes on the side of the platter and serve warm."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["30 g extra virgin olive oil","½ lemon, zest only, no white pith","50 g Parmesan cheese, crust removed and cut into cubes (3 cm)","2 garlic cloves","40 g lemon juice (approx. 1 lemon)","100 g roasted pine nuts","20 g fresh basil, leaves only","1 pinch sea salt, to taste","500 g water","125 g Brie cheese","250 g cherry tomatoes, on a vine"]}],"id":"r89682","imageLink":"https:\/\/3.bp.blogspot.com\/-n2VUpSE6as0\/XZMun9tWrkI\/AAAAAAAAaHo\/jAt_3zHBqhESTrSeHqS8rWA5D9F_l1fqACLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_NEm8GcMppR5Mbp08.png","title":"Melted Brie with basil and lemon pesto","publishedAt":"2015-12-14T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"9.6 g","fat":"25 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"2.3 g","calories":"1159 kJ \/ 276 kcal"},"usefulItems":"baking paper, serving platter","hintsAndTricks":["Serve Melted Brie or Camembert with crackers and vegetable crudités of choice or with the <em>Herbed lavosh<\/em>.","Steaming your tomatoes on the Varoma tray will make them sweeter in flavour and softer in texture."],"basicInfo":["easy","10m","30m","6 portions"]}